synopsis: Yulemas is upon us and the Dragon Friends are celebrating the only way they know how: with a feature-length Dungeons & Dragons musical comedy that is completely unrelated for legal purposes to any existing IP.
tagline: It’s the most magical time of the year.
casting: ['Dave Harmon', 'Ben Jenkins', 'Alex Lee', 'Michael Hing', 'Simon Greiner', 'Edan Lacey', 'Tom Cardy']

synopsis: Researches with the phenomenon of rhythm. Turned attention to the possible rhythm of space - because  each space has its own internal rhythm. Film focused on the process as a rhythm, without showing the result, but the “run”, the course, the rhythm, the pace of the actions.  The creative process has become like a real rhythmic process on its own  unique dynamics.
